{"article_id":"1HpzpgfFFwUUi4tN","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump confirmed on Sunday","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"that he discussed the family of former Vice President Joe Biden during a phone call with Ukraine ' s president","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"that sits at the center of a whistleblower ' s complaint about alleged abuse of power within the White House .","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"The president argued","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"that he did not do anything wrong during the call ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"but several prominent Democratic lawmakers are calling the whistleblower complaint grounds for impeachment .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Speaking to reporters Sunday","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"before heading to a rally with Indian Prime Minister Narendra Modi ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"Trump described his July 25 conversation with Ukrainian president Volodymyr Zelensky as \" perfect. \"","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"The Wall Street Journal recently reported","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"that Trump attempted eight times on the call to pressure the foreign leader to launch an investigation into Biden ' s son , Hunter , and his business ties to Ukraine , an allegation","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"that Trump has firmly denied .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"The conversation was \" largely [ about ] the fact","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"that we don ' t want our people like Vice President Biden and his son creating to the corruption already in the Ukraine , \"","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"Trump told the gathered reporters .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"Trump ,","depth":15},{"id":16,"text":"looking very red ,","depth":15},{"id":17,"text":"basically admits","depth":14},{"id":18,"text":"he asked Ukrainian President Zelensky to look into Biden during call","depth":14},{"id":19,"text":"that 's part of whistleblower complaint :","depth":14},{"id":20,"text":"`` It was largely [ about ] fact","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"that we do n't want our people like VP Biden & his son creating to the corruption largely in Ukraine ''","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"pic.twitter.com/2hvkTbHSJl","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"- Aaron Rupar","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"( @ atrupar )","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"September 22 , 2019","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"Later , he told reporters","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"he \" had every right to \" bring up Biden","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"because \" we don ' t want a country","depth":13},{"id":29,"text":"that we ' re giving massive aid to","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"to be corrupting our system . \"","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"That aid is central to questions over Trump ' s call :","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"$ 250 million in assistance had been due to that country over the summer .","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"Its release had been delayed ,","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"but Trump agreed to send it to Ukraine this month ,","depth":15},{"id":35,"text":"facing pressure from Congress .","depth":15},{"id":36,"text":"That money has the president ' s critics concerned","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"he withheld the aid in an attempt","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"to convince his Ukrainian counterpart to investigate Biden .","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"Biden is a leading frontrunner for the Democratic presidential nomination","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"and damaging information could hurt his candidacy .","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"There is absolutely no evidence","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"he was involved in his son ' s business dealings in Ukraine ,","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"nor is there evidence","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"that he did anything illegal ,","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"despite President Trump ' s suggestions otherwise .","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"Biden has called for a transcript of the phone call to be released ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"saying in a statement","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"that the alleged behavior is evidence","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"\" there is truly no bottom to President Trump ' s willingness","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"to abuse his power","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"and abase his country . \"","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"Trump signaled","depth":13},{"id":53,"text":"he is open to doing so Sunday in Houston , Texas ,","depth":13},{"id":54,"text":"telling reporters","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"\" it would be fine \" to release the transcript ;","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"he also said","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"he might \" give it to a respected source ,","depth":14},{"id":58,"text":"they can look at it , \"","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"but did not specify","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"whether he meant a news source","depth":15},{"id":61,"text":"he sees as credible","depth":15},{"id":62,"text":"or to someone within the government .","depth":14},{"id":63,"text":"He again stood by his words , however ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"saying of the transcript ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"\" what I said was so good ...","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"everybody will say that . \"","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"As Republicans defend Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"some Democrats are calling for impeachment","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Democrats aren ' t so sure","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"that what the president said was \" so good. \"","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"Many are concerned","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"he may have attempted to use his office","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"to have a foreign country interfere in the 2020 election","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"by providing some sort of opposition research in exchange for aid .","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"And","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"as reports and details about that complaint have emerged over the last week ,","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"many Democrats have begun calling for consequences , up to and including impeachment .","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"Impeachment \" may be the only remedy , \"","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"Rep. Adam Schiff","depth":15},{"id":80,"text":"( D-CA ) ,","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"who chairs the House Intelligence Committee","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"and has not previously come out in support of impeachment ,","depth":15},{"id":83,"text":"said on CNN ' s State of the Union on Sunday .","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"Schiff is a key figure in concerns about the president ' s actions on the call :","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"He is the person","depth":15},{"id":86,"text":"who called for the release of the whistleblower report","depth":15},{"id":87,"text":"after Acting Director of National Intelligence Maguire failed to disclose it to Congress ,","depth":15},{"id":88,"text":"as required by law ,","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"and his committee will investigate the allegations","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"the president faces .","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"If the whistleblower complaint is accurate","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"it \" would be ,","depth":16},{"id":93,"text":"I think ,","depth":16},{"id":94,"text":"the most profound violation of the presidential oath of office , certainly during this presidency ,","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"which says a lot , \"","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"Schiff added .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"On NBC ' s Meet the Press , Sen. Chris Murphy","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"( D-CA )","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"agreed","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"that Congress had to take the allegation seriously .","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"\" If we do have the evidence from this whistleblower","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"that the president indeed did try to bully a foreign power into affecting our elections ,","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"then we have to do something about it , \"","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"Some Democratic presidential candidates , like Sen. Elizabeth Warren and former HUD Secretary Julián Castro , argue","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"that what Democrats should do is to begin impeachment proceedings .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"Biden has not joined these calls ,","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"despite his prominence within the whole affair","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"- instead , he has said","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"Trump must be investigated .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"Biden ' s response is in line with that of House Speaker Nancy Pelosi ,","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"who came out against the idea of impeachment on Friday .","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"On Sunday , she released a \" Dear Colleagues \" letter","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"saying","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"that she expected Acting Director of National Intelligence Joseph Maguire to turn the full whistleblower complaint over to Congress ,","depth":13},{"id":116,"text":"and called on Republicans to support the investigation into the matter .","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"\" If the Administration persists in blocking this whistleblower from disclosing to Congress a serious possible breach of constitutional duties by the President ,","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"they will be entering a grave new chapter of lawlessness","depth":13},{"id":119,"text":"which will take us into a whole new stage of investigation , \"","depth":13},{"id":120,"text":"the letter reads in part .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"On Twitter , Rep. Alexandria Ocasio Cortez","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"( D-NY )","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"argued","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"her fellow Democrats ought to take a tougher stance on the complaint ,","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"writing","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"that the Democratic failure","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"to coalesce around impeachment","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"was worse than the behavior itself :","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"At this point , the bigger national scandal isn ' t the president ' s lawbreaking behavior","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"- it is the Democratic Party ' s refusal","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"to impeach him for it .","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"- Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"( @ AOC )","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"September 22 , 2019","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"She faced some criticism for that assessment ,","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"but defended her stance","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"by saying ,","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"\" It is one thing for a sitting president to break the law .","depth":15},{"id":139,"text":"It ' s another to let him . \"","depth":15},{"id":140,"text":"It is one thing for a sitting president to break the law .","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"It ' s another to let him .","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"The integrity of our democracy isn ' t threatened","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"when a president breaks the law .","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"It ' s threatened","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"when we do nothing about it .","depth":12},{"id":146,"text":"The GOP ' s silence & refusal","depth":12},{"id":147,"text":"to act","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"shouldn ' t be a surprise .","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"Ours is .","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"- Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"( @ AOC )","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"September 22 , 2019","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"Republicans responded to criticism of the president","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"by standing by his claim","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"that he ' s done nothing wrong","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"and by attempting to turn attention on Biden .","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin denied any kind of improper attempt","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"to trade aid money for an investigation into the Bidens on Meet the Press ,","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"and said","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"the fact","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"Ukraine received $ 140 million in aid on top of the promised $ 250 million","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"it was not expecting","depth":14},{"id":163,"text":"did not mean that country was given a bonus","depth":13},{"id":164,"text":"for agreeing to investigate Biden .","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"\" There was no connection , \"","depth":11},{"id":166,"text":"Mnuchin said .","depth":11},{"id":167,"text":"When host Chuck Todd then pressed Mnuchin on the additional aid money ,","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"Mnuchin dismissed that as \" details . \"","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"Mnuchin does n't have a response","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"when Chuck Todd asks him","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"if he can explain","depth":14},{"id":172,"text":"`` how all of the sudden","depth":15},{"id":173,"text":"when the [ Ukraine ] aid got released ,","depth":16},{"id":174,"text":"more money showed up .","depth":16},{"id":175,"text":"Where did [ it ] come from ? ...","depth":14},{"id":176,"text":"They got an additional $ 140m","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"they did n't expect '' `","depth":12},{"id":178,"text":"` You 're getting into details ''","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"Mnuchin says","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"pic.twitter.com/quJC8NHHC8","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"- Aaron Rupar","depth":8},{"id":182,"text":"( @ atrupar )","depth":8},{"id":183,"text":"September 22 , 2019","depth":7},{"id":184,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham told Fox News on Sunday","depth":9},{"id":185,"text":"he believes","depth":10},{"id":186,"text":"there should be an investigation into Biden","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"- a domestic one .","depth":11},{"id":188,"text":"\" I ' m calling for somebody in the Justice Department to look at all things Ukraine , \"","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"Graham said .","depth":10},{"id":190,"text":"\" I ' m hoping","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"the Department of Justice will look at the Biden-Ukraine connection ,","depth":11},{"id":192,"text":"like we looked at the Trump-Russia connection . \"","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"House Leader Kevin McCarthy also referenced the investigation into Russia in an appearance on Fox News on Friday ,","depth":8},{"id":194,"text":"and claimed","depth":10},{"id":195,"text":"Democrats are working to distract the public from scrutinizing Biden ' s record :","depth":10},{"id":196,"text":"\" Wouldn ' t it be interesting politically ,","depth":11},{"id":197,"text":"if you wanted people not to look at what Biden was doing ,","depth":11},{"id":198,"text":"to try to bring something once again alleged against this president ,","depth":11},{"id":199,"text":"as they ' ve done time and again","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"because they don ' t like the outcome of an election . \"","depth":12},{"id":201,"text":"While many Republicans circled the wagons ,","depth":7},{"id":202,"text":"at least one","depth":11},{"id":203,"text":"- Sen. Mitt Romney -","depth":11},{"id":204,"text":"called the affair \" troubling in the extreme \" on Twitter ,","depth":10},{"id":205,"text":"and wrote ,","depth":11},{"id":206,"text":"\" Critical for the facts to come out :","depth":11},{"id":207,"text":"\" If the President asked or pressured Ukraine ' s president to investigate his political rival , either directly or through his personal attorney ,","depth":12},{"id":208,"text":"it would be troubling in the extreme .","depth":12},{"id":209,"text":"Critical for the facts to come out .","depth":11},{"id":210,"text":"- Mitt Romney","depth":10},{"id":211,"text":"( @ MittRomney )","depth":10},{"id":212,"text":"September 22 , 2019","depth":9},{"id":213,"text":"As Democrats and Republicans retreat to their habitual rhetorical corners ,","depth":8},{"id":214,"text":"a number of questions about the whistleblower ' s complaint remain :","depth":8},{"id":215,"text":"We don ' t yet know the identity of the person","depth":9},{"id":216,"text":"who made it","depth":9},{"id":217,"text":"or the details of any other other allegations","depth":9},{"id":218,"text":"it may contain .","depth":9},{"id":219,"text":"It is also unclear what kind of consequences the president would face","depth":8},{"id":220,"text":"if these allegations are found to be true ,","depth":8},{"id":221,"text":"particularly given impeachment is not , by and large , favored by voters","depth":8},{"id":222,"text":"and that it would be blocked by Republicans in the Senate .","depth":8},{"id":223,"text":"Thus far , the White House has not cooperated with any investigations into the whistleblower ' s complaint .","depth":5},{"id":224,"text":"Refusing to comply with congressional requests has been a successful tactic for the Trump administration","depth":7},{"id":225,"text":"in stalling other investigations into alleged misconduct ,","depth":7},{"id":226,"text":"and","depth":9},{"id":227,"text":"given the president has already faced accusations","depth":10},{"id":228,"text":"he conspired with a foreign power","depth":11},{"id":229,"text":"to influence an election ,","depth":11},{"id":230,"text":"he is in familiar territory .","depth":8},{"id":231,"text":"As are all Americans ,","depth":8},{"id":232,"text":"for whom the specter of foreign election interference could hang for another electoral cycle .","depth":8},{"id":233,"text":"A whistleblower in the intelligence community has sparked a political scandal","depth":4},{"id":234,"text":"involving President Trump and a pair of Bidens .","depth":4},{"id":235,"text":"Andrew Prokop explains .","depth":3},{"id":236,"text":"Looking for a quick way","depth":3},{"id":237,"text":"to keep up with the never-ending news cycle ?","depth":3},{"id":238,"text":"Host Sean Rameswaram will guide you through the most important stories at the end of each day .","depth":3},{"id":239,"text":"Subscribe on Apple Podcasts , Spotify , Overcast , or wherever you listen to podcasts .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":479,"left":475,"right":478,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":475,"left":472,"right":474,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":472,"left":423,"right":471,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent